<h2>Map Refresh</h2>

<p class="medium-7 large-5">
  The <span class="gmaps-inline-code">refresh</span> method takes a map instance and triggers a reloading of that google map instance. Useful when a Map's container element resizes and new map tiles must be loaded.
</p>

<button class="th-google-button--small -mb"
  {{action "refresh"}}
  disabled={{disableButton}}>
  Resize & Refresh Map
</button>

<span class="-rel" style="top: -7px; left: 5px;">{{mapState}}</span>

<div id="resize-parent-container" style="width: 50%;" class="grid-content -np -mb">
  {{g-maps class="gmaps-docs-map" name="gmaps-refresh-map" lat=lat lng=lng zoom=zoom}}
</div>

